OL,1,D]S737{kkkc5FCost-of-living payments    
OL,2,D]S555{jjj25Fbranded insufficient as    
OL,3,D]Suuu{rrzq5Fenergy bills soar          
OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, Ministers must offer bigger            
OL,6, cost-of-living support payments as     
OL,7, energy bills are expected to soar      
OL,8, further this winter, a committee of MPs
OL,9, has said.                              
OL,11,FFinancial help for the vulnerable and  
OL,12,Fpoor needed to be "updated" to reflect 
OL,13,Fhigher bills in October, they said.    
OL,15,FWitnesses told the Business Committee: 
OL,16,F"If you think things are bad now,      
OL,17,Fyou've not seen anything yet."         
OL,19,FIts report also called energy regulator
OL,20,FOfgem "incompetent". Ofgem said it was 
OL,21,Fworking hard to reform the market.     
